# Test-only environment (loaded by Vitest, which runs in `test` mode).
# Mode-specific env files override the generic `.env`, so this pins the API
# client to a RELATIVE base. The MSW handlers in src/test/msw-handlers.ts are
# registered as `/api/...` and resolve against the jsdom origin; a real
# absolute VITE_API_BASE_URL (from `.env`) would make requests bypass them
# and hit the network, failing every API-backed test with "Network error".
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api
